ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MAHALIA VERNA of Westmount, Quebec, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of History, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Andrea T. Bobkowicz, whose term has expired.
